name: GKVoiceChatServiceError.Code
desc: Error codes for the GKVoiceChatService error domain.

items.name: case internalError
items.desc: A serious error occurred inside the voice chat service.

items.name: case noRemotePacketsError
items.desc: The voice chat service stopped receiving packets from the remote participant.

items.name: case unableToConnectError
items.desc: The voice chat service was unable to establish a connection with another user.

items.name: case remoteParticipantHangupError
items.desc: The remote participant in a voice chat stopped the chat.

items.name: case invalidCallIDError
items.desc: The voice chat service didnâ€™t recognize the call identifier.

items.name: case audioUnavailableError
items.desc: The audio hardware is unavailable to the voice chat service.

items.name: case uninitializedClientError
items.desc: The application did not set a client before calling voice chat service methods.

items.name: case clientMissingRequiredMethodsError
items.desc: The voice chat service did not find an expected method defined by the client.

items.name: case remoteParticipantBusyError
items.desc: The remote participant is already connected to a voice chat.

items.name: case remoteParticipantCancelledError
items.desc: A remote participant attempted to start a voice chat, then canceled.

items.name: case remoteParticipantResponseInvalidError
items.desc: Invalid data was received from a remote participant.

items.name: case remoteParticipantDeclinedInviteError
items.desc: A remote participant declined an invitation.

items.name: case methodCurrentlyInvalidError
items.desc: A method on the voice chat service was called when it was not allowed to be called (for example, attempting to connect when the voice chat service was already connected).

items.name: case networkConfigurationError
items.desc: The voice chat service had problems accessing the network.

items.name: case unsupportedRemoteVersionError
items.desc: The other participant is running a different version of the voice chat service.

items.name: case outOfMemoryError
items.desc: The voice chat service was unable to allocate memory required to operate.

items.name: case invalidParameterError
items.desc: A parameter had an unrecognized value.
